Invocation Name: commodore robot
des:
Using Amazon Alexa, the COMMODORE Robot vacuum cleaner skill allows you to interact, monitor and control yourCOMMODORE Robot Vacuum Cleaner by using voice commands.
To get started, you will need to link your COMMODORE Robot skill with your app account.
Once linked, you can use voice commands to control your COMMODORE Robot Vacuum Cleaner.
For instance, you can try the below voice commands:
 Alexa, ask COMMODORE Robot to start cleaning.
 Alexa, ask COMMODORE Robot to stop cleaning.
 Alexa, ask COMMODORE Robot to start charging.
